    • getItem

      public InnerMessagingItem getItem()
      generic access to the inner item. depending on the inner elements the corresponding element is returned. So you can get an OptinItem, PostbackItem, DeliveryItem, AccountLinkingItem or MessageItem
      Returns:
      the inner item.
